title: 2009 Grote Prijs Jef Scherens
text: The 2009 Grote Prijs Jef Scherens was the 43rd edition of the <a href="Grote%20Prijs%20Jef%20Scherens">Grote Prijs Jef Scherens</a> cycle race and was held on 6 September 2009. The race started and finished in <a href="Leuven">Leuven</a>. The race was won by <a href="Sebastian%20Langeveld">Sebastian Langeveld</a>.
